Class BasketBallPlayer

java.lang.Object
Player
BasketBallPlayer
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable
public class BasketBallPlayer
extends Player
implements java.lang.Comparable
BasketBallPlayer is a subclass of Player that is setup to hold values and methods for basketball plays who can be managed within a BasketBallTeam class
